WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:15.000
Downloaded From AnimeArcadia.lk

00:06.146 --> 00:08.146
[eerie, unsettling music playing]

00:26.896 --> 00:27.896
[music trails off]

00:32.105 --> 00:33.605
[somber music playing]

00:39.855 --> 00:40.980
[muffled thud]

01:01.813 --> 01:04.313
[uneasy undertones building]

01:40.105 --> 01:41.105
[restrained sobbing]

01:48.105 --> 01:50.230
["Ghost" by GUNSHIP & Power Glove playing]

01:50.313 --> 01:52.313
[mysterious synthwave music playing]

01:54.480 --> 01:55.688
[buzzer buzzing]

02:08.688 --> 02:10.188
[foreboding chords swell]

02:10.771 --> 02:14.313
♪ Molten bloody earth ♪

02:16.230 --> 02:19.188
♪ A focused open wound ♪

02:20.980 --> 02:24.438
♪ All highways lead right here ♪

02:26.980 --> 02:30.938
♪ Ghost ♪

02:43.980 --> 02:45.688
[no audible dialogue]

02:53.771 --> 02:57.230
♪ Dancing around my head ♪

02:59.063 --> 03:02.771
♪ Glowing stems of death ♪

03:04.563 --> 03:08.438
♪ Time is time again ♪

03:09.980 --> 03:14.021
♪ Ghost ♪

03:14.105 --> 03:15.230
[music swells]

03:15.313 --> 03:16.563
♪ Anodyne ♪

03:17.480 --> 03:21.230
♪ You move like heaven ♪

03:21.313 --> 03:23.313
[epic synthwave swells]

03:26.021 --> 03:30.980
♪ Physical comfort, drift away ♪

03:36.771 --> 03:41.771
♪ Anodyne distortion has
Brought us back together ♪

03:47.230 --> 03:52.938
♪ Operation Overlife, guide us away ♪

04:03.188 --> 04:04.188
[music trails off]

04:06.855 --> 04:08.521
[distressing music building]

04:13.688 --> 04:14.688
[echoing thud]

04:19.271 --> 04:21.521
[agitated metal music playing]

05:01.771 --> 05:02.771
[music trails off]

05:06.396 --> 05:08.855
[gentle, enchanting music playing]

05:25.563 --> 05:28.105
[hopeful synth music swells]

06:45.980 --> 06:47.980
[tender, uplifting music playing]

07:24.521 --> 07:26.521
[coughing silently]

08:08.771 --> 08:09.771
[music trails off]

08:09.855 --> 08:11.605
[coughing]

08:15.480 --> 08:17.480
[tense, distressing music playing]

09:18.480 --> 09:19.480
[coughing]

09:32.396 --> 09:35.063
["Afterlife" by Alex Seaver
and Amy Lee playing]

09:36.563 --> 09:38.521
[moody goth rock playing]

09:39.938 --> 09:41.521
♪ Hide ♪

09:43.855 --> 09:46.271
♪ Before the flood gates open ♪

09:46.355 --> 09:51.021
♪ Can we just lie here
Till it's all over? ♪

09:51.105 --> 09:53.605
♪ I hear the violence calling ♪

09:53.688 --> 09:56.938
♪ Soon it flows inside ♪

09:57.771 --> 10:01.438
♪ You build your walls again, again ♪

10:01.521 --> 10:05.230
♪ The faith you hide ♪

10:05.313 --> 10:08.396
♪ Down with you ♪

10:08.480 --> 10:12.813
♪ In the afterlife ♪

10:12.896 --> 10:19.855
♪ Save me from this fate
I feel I have inside ♪

10:19.938 --> 10:26.938
♪ You wonder why
I'm all out of tears to cry ♪

10:27.438 --> 10:33.021
♪ Today, I'm not afraid to die ♪

10:51.313 --> 10:52.605
♪ You wonder why ♪

10:52.688 --> 10:58.271
♪ I'm all out of tears to cry ♪

10:58.813 --> 11:03.646
♪ Today, I'm not afraid to die ♪

11:06.063 --> 11:08.146
[song trails off]

11:19.438 --> 11:21.771
[somber, mournful music playing]

11:36.730 --> 11:39.438
[measured, mournful music building]

12:27.146 --> 12:28.146
[music trails off]

12:30.480 --> 12:31.855
["Dark All Day" by GUNSHIP playing]

12:31.938 --> 12:33.771
[steely, resolute
electronic music playing]

13:06.563 --> 13:07.563
[portal warbling]

13:20.605 --> 13:24.521
♪ As he takes from me my last breath ♪

13:25.813 --> 13:27.980
♪ Inhale ♪

13:30.021 --> 13:34.688
♪ I'm picking up the scent ♪

13:39.438 --> 13:40.438
[baby coos]

13:41.605 --> 13:42.646
[babbles sweetly]

13:49.730 --> 13:51.896
♪ What a hell of a day ♪

13:53.188 --> 13:55.813
♪ To embrace disorder ♪

13:57.355 --> 14:01.563
♪ And there is something
In your eyes that burns ♪

14:03.730 --> 14:05.730
♪ What a hell of a feeling ♪

14:07.146 --> 14:08.896
♪ With such a brilliant mind ♪

14:10.438 --> 14:16.021
♪Can you feel those chemicals
In the air tonight? ♪

14:32.813 --> 14:33.813
[music trails off]

14:34.480 --> 14:36.146
[ominous synthwave music playing]

15:04.355 --> 15:05.355
[gun cocks]

15:05.438 --> 15:06.438
[guns cocking]

15:07.521 --> 15:09.355
[menacing rock music playing]

15:19.813 --> 15:20.730
[music trails off]

15:25.146 --> 15:27.146
[suspenseful music pulsing]

15:28.105 --> 15:30.105
[energy crackling]

16:08.313 --> 16:10.063
[suspenseful music intensifying]

16:11.855 --> 16:12.896
Hold!

16:12.980 --> 16:13.980
[music halts]

16:14.063 --> 16:16.355
[refugees stammering]

16:16.938 --> 16:19.313
You, why do you look human?

16:19.396 --> 16:20.396
I am human.

16:20.480 --> 16:23.146
Please, we mean no harm.

16:23.230 --> 16:25.355
We're just trying to get to safety.

16:25.438 --> 16:27.188
-There's a--
-Safety?

16:27.271 --> 16:29.730
You're smuggling demons into our realm.

16:29.813 --> 16:32.230
Our only safety
is their species' extinction.

16:32.313 --> 16:34.188
You don't understand!

16:34.271 --> 16:37.521
If you'll put the guns down,
I can explain.

16:38.480 --> 16:39.480
[panicked clamoring]

16:39.563 --> 16:41.355
[predator demon snarling]

16:41.438 --> 16:42.813
[refugees screaming]

16:46.605 --> 16:47.480
[bellows]

16:47.563 --> 16:48.688
[epic music playing]

17:06.021 --> 17:08.188
DARKCOM, evacuate!

17:33.105 --> 17:35.105
[epic music ends]

18:06.313 --> 18:08.230
[sobbing]

18:17.271 --> 18:18.271
[delirious laughter]

18:27.105 --> 18:29.438
[tense, uneasy music playing]

18:57.188 --> 19:02.771
Now, we all
go down the rabbit hole together.

19:08.438 --> 19:09.438
["Devils Never Cry" plays]

19:09.521 --> 19:10.896
♪ Bless me ♪

19:10.980 --> 19:16.980
♪ With the leaf off of the tree ♪

19:17.063 --> 19:20.896
♪ On it, I see ♪

19:20.980 --> 19:24.855
♪ The freedom reign ♪

19:24.938 --> 19:28.730
♪ We are falling ♪

19:28.813 --> 19:32.563
♪ The light is calling ♪

19:32.646 --> 19:36.480
♪ Tears inside me ♪

19:36.563 --> 19:40.438
♪ Calm me down ♪

19:40.521 --> 19:44.230
♪ Midnight calling ♪

19:44.313 --> 19:48.146
♪ Mist of resolving ♪

19:48.230 --> 19:50.188
♪ Crown me ♪

19:50.271 --> 19:56.021
♪ With the pure, green leaf ♪

19:56.105 --> 19:59.896
♪ Praise to my father ♪

19:59.980 --> 20:03.813
♪ Blessed by the water ♪

20:03.896 --> 20:06.438
♪ Black light, dark sky ♪

20:06.521 --> 20:08.021
IN MEMORY OF KEVIN CONROY
(1955-2022)

20:08.105 --> 20:12.563
♪ The devil's cry ♪